Compile lines at the end of the .cpp files
If none (.C files), call them with root because they are pure ROOT macros

To compile with make:
> make clean
> make -j4

make options:
TRIGGER="-DTRIGGER=[TriggerName]" (Read Triggers/)

Update using:
> sh UPDATE.sh

- General purpose tools : 

caen2root                   Converts .caendat raw datafile into time-ordered and event-built root file
Tools/caendatInspect        Dumps raw data from .caendat datafile in the terminal
Tools/caendatIntegrityCheck Checks if the raw .caendat datafile is not corrupted
macros/Miscellaneous.C      Collection of tree analysis created by caen2root (examples, timeshifts, spectra, special requests ...)

- Special tools :

writeTraces    Writes the traces in TGraphs with CFD
studyCFD       After event-building, checks the time correlations between detectors